Author: saerdnaa
Title: [ANN][ICO][BOUNTY] ICOStart - Rocket Startup for your ICO
Body: ICOStart Bounty Program    ICOStart will reserve 7% of all issued ICH tokens for bounty program. You can check the bounty distribution in the image above. You need to be registered to the ICOStart website to join bounty program   Facebook Bounty How to: -Like ICOStart Facebook Page -Minimum one costructive post per week, with icostart.ch website link and #BLOCKCHAIN and #ICOSTART hashtags -Fill the form   Twitter Bounty How to: -Follow ICOStart Twitter account -Minimum one costructive tweet or retweet per week, with icostart.ch website link and #BLOCKCHAIN and #ICOSTART hashtags -Fill the form   Telegram Bounty How to: -Join Telegram Chat and Telegram Channel -Minimum one costructive message per week -Fill the form   Linkedin Bounty How to: -Follow ICOStart Linkedin page -Minimum one costructive post or ICOStart repost per week, with icostart.ch website link and #BLOCKCHAIN and #ICOSTART hashtags -Fill the form   Youtube Bounty How to: -Follow ICOStart Youtube page -Minimum one good quality video, talking abount ICOStart ICO and services -Include ICOStart website link in the video details -Fill the form   BitcoinTalk Bounty How to: -Jr. Member + status needed -Minimum one costructive post per week, including ICOStart website link -Post must be more than 75 types, describing ICOStart ICO and services -Fill the form   Medium Bounty Due to new medium restrictions on ICO and cryptocurrencies in general, medium bounty program is canceled. Tokens will be distributed to telegram and linkedin campaigns!  Website | Whitepaper EN | One Page Paper | Bounty | Facebook | Twitter | Linkedin | Telegram Chat
